---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---
<Layout region="uk" title="Pricing – Alturascope UK">
  <section id="pricing" class="py-16 lg:py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-4xl">
          Pricing – Alturascope UK
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-base text-slate-600">
          Transparent, all-inclusive pricing in GBP for sites across the United Kingdom. Typical
          travel costs (road, rail, local taxis) are included in every visit, so you see one number
          and know your exposure up front.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-xs text-slate-500">
          Pricing below applies to typical commercial sites up to
          <span class="font-semibold">10,000 sq ft</span> across mainland UK. Larger or unusually
          complex facilities, very remote locations, or sites requiring overnight stays may be
          quoted separately. In rare cases where travel falls outside normal patterns, incremental
          costs may be passed through at cost and agreed with you in advance.
        </p>
      </div>
      <!-- Single visit card -->
      <div class="mt-10">
        <h2 class="text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-500">
          Single-visit option
        </h2>
        <div class="mt-4 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-[minmax(0,2fr)_minmax(0,3fr)]">
          <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition-colors hover:border-accent hover:ring-2 hover:ring-accent/30 hover:shadow-md hover:shadow-accent/20">
            <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between gap-3">
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">
                  Site Reality Pack &mdash; Single Visit (Basic)
                </h3>
                <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600">
                  One-off visit when you need visuals and key facts without committing
                  to a bundle.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="text-right">
                <p class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500">From</p>
                <p class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900">
                  £850
                </p>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">per visit</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5 text-sm text-slate-700">
              <li>Weekday, daytime visit for a single site (up to 10,000 sq ft).</li>
              <li>Core photo set and 360&deg; / digital twin walkthrough.</li>
              <li>Headline fixture &amp; services counts (lights, diffusers, sprinklers, WCs, key equipment).</li>
              <li>
                Concise snapshot report summarising key conditions, upsides, and concerns.
              </li>
              <li class="font-medium">
                Ideal for quick checks and simple decisions &mdash; heavier reporting
                and drone coverage available as add-ons.
              </li>
            </ul>

            <p class="mt-4 text-xs text-slate-500">
              "From" pricing assumes typical commercial sites in major markets, up to
              10,000 sq ft, with weekday access. Remote or complex sites, night/weekend
              access, enhanced narrative reporting, drone capture, and stakeholder
              representation may be quoted at a higher rate and agreed in advance.
            </p>

            <p class="mt-2 text-xs text-slate-500">
              Rush delivery is billed at <span class="font-semibold">+25%</span> of the
              applicable visit rate. Night (6pm&ndash;6am) or weekend access is billed
              at <span class="font-semibold">+50%</span>.
            </p>
          </article>
          <!-- What's included in every visit -->
          <article class="rounded-2xl border border-dashed border-slate-300 bg-slate-50/80 p-6 transition-colors hover:border-accent hover:ring-2 hover:ring-accent/30 hover:shadow-md hover:shadow-accent/20">
            <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-700">
              Included in every visit
            </h3>
            <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5 text-sm text-slate-700">
              <li>Pre-visit coordination with your team and building / site management.</li>
              <li>On-site capture of architectural, MEP, and access conditions.</li>
              <li>Digital twin or 360&deg; walkthrough for remote stakeholders.</li>
              <li>Labeled photo set covering shell, core, services, and issues.</li>
              <li>
                Fixture &amp; services counts appropriate to the level of service
                (snapshot for Basic single visits; full counts for bundles).
              </li>
              <li>
                Option to operate fully <span class="font-semibold">white-label</span> as part of your team
                (logo, templates, PPE, and email signature aligned to your brand).
              </li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-slate-500">
              Full narrative reporting, drone coverage, and stakeholder representation
              are <span class="font-semibold">included in monthly bundles</span> and
              available as add-ons to single visits.
            </p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- Monthly bundles -->
      <div class="mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-500">
          Monthly bundles (United Kingdom)
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
          For landlords, funds, and occupiers running multiple projects a month across the U.K.,
          bundled capacity makes planning simple. Each bundle includes a set number of full visits;
          extra visits are billed at a flat per-visit rate.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-6 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
          <!-- 8 visits -->
          <article class="flex h-full flex-col rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition-colors hover:border-accent hover:shadow-md hover:shadow-accent/20">
            <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between gap-3">
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">
                  Core 8 (UK)
                </h3>
                <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600">
                  For steady regional activity across the U.K.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="text-right">
                <p class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-500">
                  8 visits / month
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-4 flex items-baseline gap-1">
              <p class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900">
                £9,600
              </p>
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">/ month</p>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">
              Effective rate: £1,200 per visit
            </p>
            <ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5 text-sm text-slate-700">
              <li>Up to 8 full site visits / month (each up to 10,000 sq ft)</li>
              <li>Mainland U.K. coverage; typical road/rail/local taxis included</li>
              <li>Any visit type (As-Built, Progress, Diligence)</li>
              <li>Priority scheduling within 10 business days</li>
              <li>Extra visits: <span class="font-medium">£1,600 / visit</span></li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-slate-500">
              Rush delivery is billed at +25% of the applicable visit rate.
              Night (6pm–6am) or weekend access is billed at +50%.
            </p>
          </article>
          <!-- 10 visits (featured) -->
          <article class="flex h-full flex-col rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition-colors hover:border-accent hover:shadow-md hover:shadow-accent/20">
            <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between gap-3">
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">
                  Growth 10 (UK)
                </h3>
                <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600">
                  Ideal for active portfolios across multiple U.K. markets.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="text-right">
                <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-primary border border-accent px-3 py-1 text-[11px] font-medium uppercase tracking-wide text-white">
                  Most popular
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-4 flex items-baseline gap-1">
              <p class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">
                £10,000
              </p>
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">/ month</p>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">
              Effective rate: £1,000 per visit
            </p>
            <ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5 text-sm text-slate-700">
              <li>Up to 10 full site visits / month (each up to 10,000 sq ft)</li>
              <li>Mainland U.K. coverage; typical road/rail/local taxis included</li>
              <li>Mix and match visit types as needed</li>
              <li>Priority scheduling within 7 business days</li>
              <li>Extra visits: <span class="font-semibold">£1,600 / visit</span></li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-slate-500">
              Rush delivery is billed at +25% of the applicable visit rate.
              Night (6pm–6am) or weekend access is billed at +50%.
            </p>
          </article>
          <!-- 12 visits -->
          <article class="flex h-full flex-col rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm transition-colors hover:border-accent hover:shadow-md hover:shadow-accent/20">
            <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between gap-3">
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">
                  Portfolio 12 (UK)
                </h3>
                <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600">
                  For continuous roll-outs and national U.K. programmes.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="text-right">
                <p class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-500">
                  12 visits / month
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-4 flex items-baseline gap-1">
              <p class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-slate-900">
                £10,800
              </p>
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">/ month</p>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">
              Effective rate: £900 per visit
            </p>
            <ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5 text-sm text-slate-700">
              <li>Up to 12 full site visits / month (each up to 10,000 sq ft)</li>
              <li>Mainland U.K. coverage; typical road/rail/local taxis included</li>
              <li>Designed for multi-site, multi-region portfolios</li>
              <li>Top-priority scheduling within 5 business days</li>
              <li>Extra visits: <span class="font-medium">£1,600 / visit</span></li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-slate-500">
              Rush delivery is billed at +25% of the applicable visit rate.
              Night (6pm–6am) or weekend access is billed at +50%.
            </p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- Add-ons and notes -->
      <div class="mt-10 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
        <!-- Stakeholder Walkthrough & Trade Day (UK) -->
        <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 transition-colors hover:border-accent hover:shadow-md hover:shadow-accent/20">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-700">
            Stakeholder Walkthrough &amp; Trade Day (UK)
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-700">
            On-site representation with your brokers, clients, landlords, and trades to align scope,
            budgets, and expectations around the real space.
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5 text-sm text-slate-700">
            <li>Hosted walkthroughs with brokers, client reps, and/or landlords</li>
            <li>Coordinated trade walk to support accurate pricing and scope clarity</li>
            <li>Live clarification of structural, services, access, and base-build issues</li>
            <li>Concise follow-up summary with key agreements, open items, and cost risks</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-slate-500">
            From <span class="font-semibold">£1,000</span> as a half-day add-on when combined with a
            Site Reality, Progress, or Diligence visit. Standalone representation days can be quoted
            separately based on location and agenda.
          </p>
        </article>
        <!-- Drone photo & video add-on (UK) -->
        <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-6 transition-colors hover:border-accent">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-700">
            Drone photo &amp; video add-on (UK)
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-700">
            Add focused aerial coverage to any visit (where legal and safe to fly under U.K. rules).
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-1 pl-5 text-sm text-slate-700">
            <li>High-resolution roof &amp; site stills</li>
            <li>Context views of parking, access, loading, neighbours</li>
            <li>Short raw video clips for internal updates &amp; investor decks</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-slate-500">
            Priced per visit based on location, airspace restrictions, and permissions. Included in
            your quote before we mobilise.
          </p>
        </article>
        <!-- Custom retainers & enterprise (UK) -->
        <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 transition-colors hover:border-accent hover:shadow-md hover:shadow-accent/20">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-700">
            Custom retainers &amp; enterprise (UK)
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-700">
            Running more than 12 sites a month across the U.K., or working across multiple business
            units?
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-700">
            We can structure a portfolio retainer aligned to your pipeline and reporting cadence,
            including standardised templates, integration with your PM tools, and custom deliverables
            for investors and lenders.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-slate-500">
            Talk to us about your portfolio and we’ll recommend a simple structure that protects your time and budget.
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>
      <!-- CTA strip -->
      <div class="mt-12 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 px-6 py-8 sm:flex sm:items-center sm:justify-between">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900">
            Not sure which UK option fits?
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
            Share your buildings, locations, and timelines. We’ll suggest the right mix of single
            visits and bundles for the U.K., and send a clear, all-in proposal.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-3 sm:mt-0 sm:justify-end">
          <a
            href="/uk/contact"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-slate-900 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-slate-800"
          >
            Talk to Alturascope UK
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

